---
title: Cathcart United Free Church, Glasgow
description: Cathcart United Free Church, Glasgow. Growing together in Christ. Serving the community. Sharing Jesus' love.
activeNav: home
layout: base.njk
---

<!-- HERO IMAGE WITH STRAPLINE -->
<div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-placeholder">
        <img src="/assets/images/church-front-narrow-scaled.jpg" alt="Front of Cathcart UF Church" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-strapline">
        Growing together in Christ.<br />
        Serving the community.<br />
        Sharing Jesus' love.
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container">

    <!-- MINISTRY OPPORTUNITY NOTICE -->
    <div class="notice-card">
        <h3>Ministry Opportunity at Cathcart UF</h3>
        <p>We are seeking a minister to serve on a full-time or part-time basis who will help us
            in our aims of "Growing together in Christ, serving the community, sharing Jesus' love"
            through worship and preaching, pastoral care and working with us in the local community.</p>
        <p><a href="/ministry-opportunity/" class="section-link">Find out more →</a></p>
    </div>

    <!-- LATEST NEWS -->
    {% set newsItems = collections.news | activeNews %}
    {% if newsItems and newsItems.length > 0 %}
    <h2>Latest News</h2>
    {% for item in newsItems %}
    <div class="news-section">
        <div class="news-item">
            {% if item.image %}
            <div class="card-content-with-image">
                <h3>{{ item.title }}</h3>
                <div class="card-image">
                    <img src="{{ item.image }}" 
                    alt="{{ item.imageAlt }}" 
                    class="news-image-{{ item.imageSize or 'medium' }}" />
                </div>
            </div>
            {% else %}
            <h3>{{ item.title }}</h3>
            {% endif %}
            <p>{{ item.summary }}</p>
            {% if item.details %}
            {{ item.details | markdown | safe }}
            {% endif %}
            {% if item.link %}
                {% if "http" in item.link %}
                    <a href="{{ item.link }}" class="section-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ item.linkText or "Find out more" }} →</a>
                {% else %}
                    <a href="{{ item.link }}" class="section-link">{{ item.linkText or "Find out more" }} →</a>
                {% endif %}
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
    {% endif %}

    <!-- COMING UP -->
    {% set upcomingEvents = collections.events | futureEvents | limit(2) %}
    {% if upcomingEvents and upcomingEvents.length > 0 %}
    <h2>Coming Up</h2>
    <div class="coming-up">
        <div class="coming-up-list">
            {% for event in upcomingEvents %}
            <div class="coming-up-card">
                <div class="coming-up-date">
                    <strong>{{ event.date | dateDay }}</strong>
                    {{ event.date | dateMonth }}
                </div>
                <div class="coming-up-info">
                    <h4>{{ event.title }}</h4>
                    <p>{{ event.time }}
                        {% if event.location %} at {{ event.location }}{% endif %}
                        {% if event.description %} &bull; {{ event.description }}{% endif %}
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <a href="/events/" class="more-events-link">See all upcoming events →</a>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <!-- ABOUT / WHO WE ARE -->
    <h2>Welcome to Cathcart United Free Church</h2>

    <p>We are a small fellowship in Cathcart — a group of ordinary people who come together to
        share faith and hope in Jesus. With the help of God's Spirit, we seek to share the Good News
        of Jesus Christ through worship, prayer, caring and teaching within our church family and through
        outreach into our community and beyond.</p>

    <p>We are always delighted to welcome other folk — whether it be online or in-person, visiting
        or staying for a while. <a href="/contact/">Drop us a message</a> if you would like to
        find out more or just want to have a wee chat!</p>

    <!-- SCRIPTURE QUOTE -->
    <div class="scripture-card">
        <p><em>"There is neither Jew nor Greek, there is neither slave nor free, there is no male
                and female, for you are all one in Christ Jesus."</em></p>
        <p class="scripture-ref">Galatians 3:28</p>
    </div>

    <!-- FEATURE PANELS -->
    <div class="feature-panels">

        <div class="feature-panel">
            <h3>Our Meetings</h3>
            <p><strong>Sundays 11–12:15pm</strong><br />
                In-person, Zoom &amp; YouTube Livestream.<br />
                Tea and coffee after the service.</p>
            <p><strong>Wednesdays 10:30–11:15am</strong><br />
                Time for Reflection — in-person.</p>
            <div class="photo-row">
                <div class="photo-placeholder">
                    <img src="/assets/images/logo.png" alt="Midweek gathering at Cathcart United Free Church" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/meetings/" class="section-link">Find out more →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-panel">
            <h3>Prayer</h3>
            <p>We would love to pray for you. Send us your prayer request and we will
                hold you before God in prayer.</p>
            <a href="/prayer/#prayer-request">Send a prayer request</a>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-panel">
            <h3>Any Questions?</h3>
            <p>We would love to hear from you — whether you have a question, want to
                find out more, or just want to say hello.</p>
            <a href="/contact/">Contact us</a>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- DENOMINATION -->
    <div class="denomination-strip">
        <p>Cathcart United Free Church belongs to the <a href="https://ufcos.org.uk" target="_blank"
                rel="noopener">United Free Church of Scotland</a>, sharing a commitment to Reformed evangelical
            faith, Presbyterian governance, and warm fellowship.</p>
        <p>We invite you to explore the denomination's wider mission, ministries, and community work across the
            country. <a href="https://ufcos.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="section-link">Find out
                more →</a></p>
    </div>

</div>